title: Fania All Stars - With Pete ''El Conde'' Rodriguez (1998)@flac
description:
Pete "Conde" Rodriguez was the most soulful sonero ever (he could literally challenge the great soul singers with his soulful and powerful singing style). 
This compilation focuses on his work with the Fania All Stars and includes both studio-recorded and live material. His superb duet with Celia Cruz ("Encantigo") is reason enough for buying this CD but the live versions of "Pueblo Latino" and "Macho Cimarron" are also incredibly good. 
Real salsa at its best with plenty of soul and sabor! (Customer from Amazon)
